@{PARD}
@{B}MONSTERNAME Description:@{UB}@{PAR}

Rapiertails appearance is much like a wyvern and from a far distance may be
mistaken as one. Though it's smaller size and many tails give it away upon
closer inspection. They are greyish in skin colour and have reptilian like hides
which acts as effective armour. Perhaps a rapiertails most distingushed feature
is the fact it has more than one tail. Rapiertails have 2-6 tails, and the more
tails the higher it's hit dice. (Hit dice is equal to 3 + the number of tails
the creature has.)@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

